267
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:52,966
hoping to restore the order and
save these people from sufferings.

268
00:23:54,066 --> 00:23:56,733
Now, you young ruler, is absurd and fatuous.

269
00:23:57,000 --> 00:24:04,600
