superiors, I would applying all punishments to him.

278
00:24:44,533 --> 00:24:45,200
So be it.

279
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:48,566
Listen to the orders and do not disappoint me.

280
00:25:16,133 --> 00:25:17,500
